---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout title="Home" currentPath="/">
  <article>
    <h1>Movement Retraining & Resolution</h1>
    <p>Hello, and welcome. My name is <strong>Yogi Ponappa</strong>. I help musicians overcome focal hand dystonia and get back to playing again.</p>
    
    <p>If you're reading this, chances are you're a professional or advanced amateur musician, and that you've either had a diagnosis of focal hand dystonia, or are investigating some strange and disruptive involuntary finger movements and/or a lack of motor control you've been experiencing while playing your guitar, piano, violin, oboe, or other instrument. In either case, this site will be of interest to you.</p>

    <blockquote>
      "Musician's task-specific focal hand dystonia is not a disease, nor is it permanent. With the right behavioural and movement therapy, resolution is entirely possible."
    </blockquote>

    <h2>My Approach</h2>
    <p>My approach to resolving focal hand dystonia draws on proven experimental and mainstream behavioural therapies, as well as kinesiology and ergonomic instrument technique. I focus on gentle, deliberate retraining to rebuild the brain's motor maps.</p>
    
    <div class="card-grid">
      <a href={`${base}about/my-story`} class="card">
        <h3>About & Story</h3>
        <p>Learn about my personal journey overcoming focal hand dystonia and the retraining principles that guide my practice.</p>
      </a>
      
      <a href={`${base}programs`} class="card">
        <h3>Programs & Splints</h3>
        <p>Explore retraining options, customized splints, and strategies to cope and recover without medical intervention.</p>
      </a>
      
      <a href={`${base}testimonials`} class="card">
        <h3>Testimonials</h3>
        <p>Read recovery stories and see progress videos from professional guitarists who successfully returned to performing.</p>
      </a>
      
      <a href={`${base}blog/articles`} class="card">
        <h3>Blog & Articles</h3>
        <p>Read in-depth articles discussing the science, kinesiology, and insights on Focal Hand Dystonia (FHD).</p>
      </a>
    </div>

    <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
    <p>If you'd like to learn more or arrange a consultation, please visit my contact page.</p>
    <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
      <a href={`${base}contact`} class="btn">Arrange a Free Consultation</a>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
